effect was observed at 150 ppm. Since the experiment was replicated six times, 
variability in the survival times of animals in different replicates was 
studied. Although all replicates were conducted under specific pathogen free / 
defined flora (SPF/DF) conditions, a significant change in survival time was 
demonstrated across replicates.

